imdb.plot outline: Follow John (Janusz), a veteran truck driver on his journeys throughout the United States of America. He will face the heat in the west, severe storms in the mid-west, and the cruel winters of the east all while delivering the goods which keep America running. What issues lay ahead? Where will the road lead him? Find out on Trucking Thru America.
